<sect1 id="templates_page_1templates_tools">
<title>Tools Base Class</title>
<para>The <computeroutput>tools</computeroutput> class provides common utility functions inherited by most templates:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>String manipulation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>File path handling</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Hash computation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Timing utilities</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="templates_page_1templates_notification">
<title>Notification Base Class</title>
<para>The <computeroutput>notification</computeroutput> class provides logging functionality:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Message logging at various levels</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Progress reporting</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Warning and error tracking </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
